{"tid":1534472,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"831 太子 消失了的人和事    整合","createTime":"2019-09-03T04:19:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T16:55:06.000Z","uid":21410,"like":37,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":70,"replies":[{"pid":"57840f75b4e80794594b560da0988fbf25a00465","tid":1534472,"uid":21410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:19:37.000Z","msg":"因之前太多唔同 post    現嘗試張 過去 8小時的資料整合<br />\n<br />\n以現在有片的 資源下   以下呢個手足 係最大機會遇害<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bhnZmkV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbhnZmkV.jpg&h=5ee9a621&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n按以下連結<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/videos/2357551941030317/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhk.nextmedia%2Fvideos%2F2357551941030317%2F&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFCvt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=c9ee827a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/videos/2357551941030317/</a><br />\n<br />\n睇到呢位手足 係點俾隻蓄龍 撳係地下   <br />\n片中最後1秒 記者有問到佢個名   之後就斷左片   <br />\n隱約聽到 手足個名 叫 王坤  (唔肯定 大家幫下手聽下)<br />\n<br />\n之後以下呢段相同片 就係另一個記者 係另一個時段返到去同一個位<br />\n呢個時侯 位手足 估計應該 經已俾班警察 推左埋牆 又有 大約10個警察圍住   <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9vy2jdQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9vy2jdQ.png&h=a0915a9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">片係要由 大約 6:40 開始睇   </span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/videos/724119284717359?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhk.nextmedia%2Fvideos%2F724119284717359%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFCvt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=7048dfb1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/videos/724119284717359?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n大家係片裡面  會聽到  有把女聲叫左 2次  醒呀 <br />\n估計呢把女聲係 警察d FA       <br />\n<br />\n另外 大家會見到 果班 警察 個圍法 同 行為神色 都係好古怪的<br />\n呢排大家見到 一般警察咁樣圍人 大都只會  係  打緊手足  <br />\n但佢地並無任何動作  只有不斷私私細語  唔見曬一般圍手足時的 兇恨表情      <br />\n<br />\n另外 點解會話係 警察 FA  做緊野    因為見到一個帶住警察頭盔企入面 <br />\n如果係一般 FA 做野 一定會要求d警察 行開d  俾多d空間做野   <br />\n而家係遮住做 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而家請大家集中幫手 討論呢個手足先     <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n下午 會整合埋 其他資料繼續討論 <br />\n<br />\n有師兄 話  冇人失縱<br />\n唔該睇睇 以下呢2張 對話 <br />\n  <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/06jpxzQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F06jpxzQ.jpg&h=7c2c6b7b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CggWoGy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCggWoGy.jpg&h=3fa94c5c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"deb8a44c0683d92f6ea2186abc1eba0b928e9ef0","tid":1534472,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:19:43.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"92bce7dfbfd5748a5c59f2153c126a7c43ea7134","tid":1534472,"uid":5893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:22:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e87d590abcce4d6402f93559fe2c002b7c8e19f","tid":1534472,"uid":32226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:22:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bae7db69a7d3962518c82eab28e49b536e7f4018","tid":1534472,"uid":63190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:22:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"af8182621b15cbc153dc2c4473049bb3ccf04796","tid":1534472,"uid":12179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:23:18.000Z","msg":"推到申請禁制令拎CCTV"},{"pid":"c2c83d8cf5a4b77e5995bb9ffef54505bd4455d1","tid":1534472,"uid":63190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:23:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e3bb3544c4b5fe661aa75332ed13592b1c58bc92","tid":1534472,"uid":105353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:24:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5f74bc067732fc3615700a13523b62d3d1cd9185","tid":1534472,"uid":21410,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:25:41.000Z","msg":"唔記得講  :<br />\n<br />\n以上資料 全部都係 呢度巴打 分析 組合   <br />\n固此無法 FC     <br />\n<br />\n整合係為左 方便大家集中討論  返  而家大家得出結論 <br />\n希望大家 有意幫手朋友 一齊黎 分析 組合<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請先不要瘋傳</span><br />\n<br />\n大膽推理  小心求証"},{"pid":"ac0079c68349b56aafa64dc462e1191d2e2de269","tid":1534472,"uid":313354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:26:32.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔起<br />\n希望冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6baa69325e04781a5041ac8df5cf4fbd1821a45e","tid":1534472,"uid":185960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:26:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2082a58d435dbb9475233238fd98e12ef8308d65","tid":1534472,"uid":12179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f74bc067732fc3615700a13523b62d3d1cd9185","tid":1534472,"uid":21410,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:25:41.000Z","msg":"唔記得講  :<br />\n<br />\n以上資料 全部都係 呢度巴打 分析 組合   <br />\n固此無法 FC     <br />\n<br />\n整合係為左 方便大家集中討論  返  而家大家得出結論 <br />\n希望大家 有意幫手朋友 一齊黎 分析 組合<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請先不要瘋傳</span><br />\n<br />\n大膽推理  小心求証"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:27:02.000Z","msg":"岩 推到申請禁制令拎CCTV"},{"pid":"e97667af7c22bdad255f39c4476835939684e656","tid":1534472,"uid":82759,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:27:56.000Z","msg":"我正式宣布香港人要6大訴求,<br />\n要加埋解散現役警隊及重組"},{"pid":"625962b29775e614c064d5eb66ab0e8f604f26e0","tid":1534472,"uid":83989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:28:24.000Z","msg":"辛苦整合 集中討論<br />\n希望人無事"},{"pid":"fe39af276e00ecade100b0cf715a43522d35fa83","tid":1534472,"uid":272202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:28:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f812c8af0ac0b08094b51769ae65a6c4710d42ab","tid":1534472,"uid":12179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:29:24.000Z","msg":"推到申請禁制令拎CCTV<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60650c2af15adba80eeca3d4287c97d3edfbb826","tid":1534472,"uid":289649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:30:06.000Z","msg":"明白大家呢排嘅士氣經過<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">831恐襲</span></span>同<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">901大撤退</span></span>之後好低落<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我同大家一樣都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但越係呢啲時候<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地就越要堅持下去，<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">團結一致</span></span><br />\n唔好比林鄭見我地冇士氣而去捉多啲人<br />\n<br />\n以下兩篇文章<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無論<span style=\"color: gold;\">和理非</span>，定係<span style=\"color: red;\">勇武</span>，都應該入黎，打返枝<span style=\"color: violet;\">強心針</span></span><br />\n<br />\n希望可以幫到大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記得share比身邊因近日事件而唔開心嘅朋友仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［全部人同我入黎］《致眾表》望各位香港市民出自己的一份綿力<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1532967\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1532967</a><br />\n<br />\n灰心喪志，是因為你看不見抗爭的前路<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1533741\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1533741</a>"},{"pid":"84b937b2c9997425e15ba1e44326d133e3ffe89e","tid":1534472,"uid":910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:32:07.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n希望人無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4ee06868945f22396abb4f839e9ca99a98a0410","tid":1534472,"uid":107596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:32:51.000Z","msg":"唔係有樣架咩？"},{"pid":"88a9d9803b962786ffe781129b0df2fa7d300c69","tid":1534472,"uid":21410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4ee06868945f22396abb4f839e9ca99a98a0410","tid":1534472,"uid":107596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:32:51.000Z","msg":"唔係有樣架咩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:35:19.000Z","msg":"呢個手足  一路都冇 正面    <br />\n其實仲有一段 佢俾6~7個 蓄龍 係車箱拉出黎<br />\n不過當時仲係有 mask   所以係睇唔到 樣  <br />\n而我都冇特別去 搵返段片出黎"},{"pid":"c671bcb1d9973b7d9ff47f6054c991fa0acc6b26","tid":1534472,"uid":93908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:35:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83e1846cbefa3a12a22150faa855ff6a33f318c7","tid":1534472,"uid":78631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:35:47.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打整合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n推到有真相"},{"pid":"3eb6b5f79b374292d0d76617b14af251f42b877e","tid":1534472,"uid":93908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:35:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afb48a5134c047905732d6ac84543d44da4bd6eb","tid":1534472,"uid":130076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:36:59.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1db4862ae3e644d9d9ab516d544ff492ee2ab456","tid":1534472,"uid":12179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:45:23.000Z","msg":"推到申請禁制令拎CCTV"},{"pid":"e962dda14fb2ebfd97ac5a59bcb8054ba71e4da4","tid":1534472,"uid":12179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:50:00.000Z","msg":"推到申請禁制令拎CCTV"},{"pid":"03b343c92df8a3beaadc82d877800170eaa9862d","tid":1534472,"uid":52566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:51:32.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"099ed53c713c9d76c20b4a87c365ca62e4346a11","tid":1534472,"uid":82759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:52:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">六大訴求，缺一不可！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n1. 立即實行真雙普選<br />\n2. 解散並重組現役警隊<br />\n3. 成立獨立調查委員會調查警方濫權、濫捕、濫暴情況<br />\n4. 釋放所有被補義士，並作出道歉及賠償<br />\n5. 撤銷暴動定性<br />\n6. 撤回逃犯(修訂)條例草案<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命！</span></span>"},{"pid":"4404310d3ee867435b086f97ac9f7451a99f558d","tid":1534472,"uid":72058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:53:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"899ee7ab2bd88bd56cbea4ab3b6dec5f2196c3f9","tid":1534472,"uid":301432,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:54:33.000Z","msg":"巴打好詳細，而且E個應該無炒車，非死則重傷。<br />\n急尋黃坤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d55252b65f998997a021ae0903996b11fd5ef55","tid":1534472,"uid":204872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:03:09.000Z","msg":"推到申請禁制令拎CCTV<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f324084a601aeecdc8b3ffa5b14db39027fe447","tid":1534472,"uid":310535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:08:32.000Z","msg":"一定要推"},{"pid":"21835b84b3c489ebee799ac2497aa143a18596dc","tid":1534472